0oxygen%20your%20body%20can%20use%20during%20aerobic%20exercise%20%E2%80%94%20in%20other%20words%2C%20how%20well%20your%20heart%20can%20circulate%20oxygenated%20blood%20to%20your%20muscles%2C%20and%20how%20well%20your%20muscles%20can%20pull%20out%20that%20oxygen%20for%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20traditionally%20considered%20a%20marker%20of%20endurance.%20So%20you%20have%20a%20higher%20VO2%20max%2C%20you%20have%20a%20better%20endurance%20capacity%2C%26quot%3B%20Blander%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20coined%20in%201923%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fqjmed%2Farticle-abstract%2Fos-16%2F62%2F135%2F1594478%3FredirectedFrom%3Dfulltext%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBritish%20physiologists%20Archibald%20Hill%20and%20Hartley%20Lupton%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20term%20derives%20from%20the%20quantity%20in%20volume%20(the%20%26quot%3BV%26quot%3B)%2C%20oxygen%20(O2%2C%20the%20chemical%20symbol%20for%20the%20oxygen%20molecule)%2C%20and%20the%20abbreviation%20of%20%26quot%3Bmaximum.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20typically%20described%20as%20milliliters%20of%20oxygen%20consumed%20per%20minute%20per%20kilogram%20of%20body%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20VO2%20max%20of%20an%20active%20woman%20might%20be%20around%2035%20mL%2Fkg%2Fmin%2C%20according%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhealth.clevelandclinic.org%2Fwhat-is-vo2-max-and-how-to-calculate-it%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Cleveland%20Clinic%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Men%20tend%20to%20have%20a%20slightly%20higher%20VO2%20max%2C%20so%20an%20example%20for%20an%20active%20man%20could%20be%20around%2042%20mL%2Fkg%2Fmin.%20These%20numbers%20hold%20true%20to%20around%20age%2045%2C%20after%20which%20they%20start%20to%20dip.%20Unless%20you%20take%20your%20exercise%20seriously%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20possible%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-tips-older-athlete-exercise-diet-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelite%20athletes%20in%20their%2080s%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20beyond%20to%20have%20a%20VO2%20max%20as%20good%20or%20better%20than%20people%20decades%20younger.%20One%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC4348610%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2015%20case%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20found%20an%2080-year-old%20man%20with%20a%20VO2%20max%20of%2050%20mL%2Fkg%2Fmin%2C%20comparable%20to%20a%20sedentary%2020-year-old%20or%20active%2035-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20doesn't%20just%20matter%20for%20working%20out.%20How%20well%20your%20body%20uses%20oxygen%20can%20point%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkey-factors-predict-heart-health-according-to-doctors-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20well%20your%20heart%20is%20functioning%3C%2Fa%3E%20overall%2C%20and%20how%20healthy%20it%20is%20under%20stress%2C%20according%20to%20Dr.%20Edo%20Paz%2C%20a%20cardiologist%20at%20White%20Plains%20Hospital%20and%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20medical%20affairs%20at%20the%20digital%20health%20company%20Hello%20Heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222384%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20athlete%20wearing%20as%20face%20mask%20and%20running%20on%20a%20treadmill%20as%20part%20of%20a%20VO2%20max%20test%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e10d33ce7f1785b2e52078%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221257%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVO2%20max%20testing%20in%20a%20lab%20involves%20an%20uncomfortable%20process%20of%20working%20out%20hard%20to%20assess%20how%20well%20your%20heart%20can%20perform%20under%20strain.%3Cp%3EKobus%20Louw%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPaz%20said%20VO2%20max%20is%20most%20accurately%20measured%20with%20a%20stress%20test%2C%20which%20can%20also%20assess%20potential%20heart%20problems%2C%20such%20as%20issues%20with%20the%20valves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20tough%20to%20accurately%20measure%20VO2%20max%20at%20any%20given%20moment%20without%20heading%20into%20a%20lab%2C%20according%20to%20Paz%2C%20but%20you%20may%20not%20need%20to.%20Noting%20changes%20over%20time%20can%20indicate%20if%20your%20heart%20health%20is%20improving%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYour%20VO2%20max%20can%20tell%20you%20a%20lot%20about%20how%20your%20heart%20is%20aging%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVO2%20max%20can%20be%20a%20shorthand%20to%20help%20assess%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-cardio-exercise-men-can-prevent-cancer-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elower%20your%20risk%20of%20dying%20early%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20illnesses%20like%20heart%20disease%2C%20diabetes%2C%20and%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20higher%20VO2%20max%20you%20have%20a%20much%20better%20chance%20based%20on%20our%20data%20analysis%20to%20live%20better%2C%20longer%2C%20which%20is%20amazing%2C%26quot%3B%20Blander%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20to%20diversify%20my%20training%20portfolio.%20We%20need%20to%20do%20the%20majority%20of%20our%20investing%20at%20a%20lower%20intensity%20and%20some%20at%20a%20higher%20intensity%20to%20improve%20maximum%20efficiency%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20Mike%20Thomson%2C%20Life%20Time%20Overland%20Park%20personal%20trainer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EPut%20simply%2C%20it%20can%20be%20a%20single%20number%20that%20gives%20you%20a%20sense%20of%20where%20you%20stand%20in%20terms%20of%20fitness%20now%2C%20and%20the%20odds%20that%20you'll%20keep%20being%20healthy%20and%20fit%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20to%20think%20of%20it%20as%20a%20'score'%20of%20your%20cardio%20and%20fitness%20potential.%20The%20higher%20your%20score%2C%20the%20greater%20your%20longevity%2C%26quot%3B%20Mike%20Thomson%2C%20personal%20trainer%20and%20run%20coach%20at%20Life%20Time%20Overland%20Park%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVO2%20max%20also%20plays%20an%20important%20role%20in%20making%20sure%20you%20can%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20demands%20of%20day-to-day%20life%20even%20beyond%20your%20workouts%2C%20explained%20exercise%20physiologist%20Kate%20Baird.%20Your%20VO2%20max%20tends%20to%20decrease%20as%20you%20get%20older%2C%20which%20over%20time%20can%20make%20it%20harder%20to%20do%20simple%20activities%2C%20according%20to%20Baird.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20already%20at%20a%20low%20level%2C%20you'll%20start%20to%20feel%20those%20declines.%20Walking%20a%20few%20blocks%20down%20the%20street%20feels%20hard%20or%20a%20leisurely%20bike%20ride%20doesn't%20feel%20so%20leisurely%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BKeeping%20fitness%20high%20helps%20you%20maintain%20autonomy%20and%20translates%20to%20a%20longer%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20diversify%20your%20training%20portfolio%20for%20a%20stronger%20VO2%20max%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20boosting%20VO2%20max%2C%20Thomson%20also%20reached%20for%20money%20management%20as%20a%20metaphor%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-live-longer-lifestyle-habits-longevity-doctor-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheart%20health%20longevity%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20VO2%20max%20is%20your%20fitness%20retirement%20plan%2C%20training%20it%20can%20be%20similar%20to%20investing%20with%20a%20combination%20of%20strategies%20for%20best%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20to%20diversify%20my%20training%20portfolio%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20do%20the%20majority%20of%20our%20investing%20at%20a%20lower%20intensity%20and%20some%20at%20a%20higher%20intensity%20to%20improve%20maximum%20efficiency%2C%26quot%3B%20Thomson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223972%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mike%20Thomson%2C%20personal%20trainer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%