n.%20But%20now%20it%20is%20an%20open%20message%20to%20all%20that%20if%20players%20are%20available%2C%20they%20have%20to%20play%20domestic%20cricket%2C%20and%20that%20is%20how%20you%20have%20to%20protect%20this%20tournament.%20That%20is%20what%20I%20also%20said%20in%20my%20tweet.%20Now%20everyone%20should%20fall%20in%20place%2C%20not%20one%20or%20two%20individuals.%20The%20rule%20has%20to%20be%20equal%20for%20all.%20Many%20other%20things%20need%20to%20be%20looked%20at%2C%20and%20in%20time%2C%20I'll%20write%20a%20letter%20to%20BCCI%20to%20highlight%20those%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tiwary%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesnownews.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl-talk-on-ranji-field-players-faked-injuries-avoided-domestic-cricket-bcci-contract-snub-good-message-manoj-tiwary-article-108100023%5C%22%3ESports%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwary%20suggested%20that%20young%20and%20established%20players%20have%20faked%20injuries%20in%20the%20past%20to%20avoid%20playing%20domestic%20games%2C%20and%20even%20if%20they%20feature%2C%20there%20conversations%20are%20mainly%20regarding%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20seen%20youngsters%20and%20established%20players%20speak%20only%20about%20IPL%20during%20domestic%20matches.%20Even%20in%20the%20zonal%20matches%2C%20when%20I%20used%20to%20play%2C%20their%20discussions%20are%20entirely%20based%20on%20IPL%2C%20and%20that%20I%20have%20seen%20from%20close%20quarters.%20The%20conversations%2C%20topics%20and%20issues%20mostly%20surrounded%20IPL%20only%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwary%20feels%20players%20do%20prioritise%20IPL%20over%20domestic%20cricket%20due%20to%20the%20money%20factor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20pretty%20natural%20once%20IPL%20contracts%20are%20given%20before%20the%20Ranji%2C%20it%20does%20affect%20someone%20-%20when%20you%20get%205%20cr%20or%207%20cr%2C%20players%20start%20thinking%20in%20their%20subconsciousness.%20So%20when%20a%20Ranji%20match%20comes%2C%20they%20try%20to%20avoid%20the%20last%20bit%20of%20effort%20required%20to%20dive%20and%20save%20a%20boundary%20that%20might%20have%20been%20crucial%20for%20the%20domestic%20team.%20So%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20those%20have%20been%20left%20alone%2C%20avoided%2C%20and%20that%20is%20a%20fact.%20Then%20they%20try%20to%20find%20a%20reason%2C%20maybe%20a%20niggle.%20Earlier%2C%20what%20used%20to%20happen%3F%20Players%20turned%20up%20for%20their%20sides%20even%20while%20carrying%20an%20injury%2C%20but%20now%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20sit%20out%20the%20game%20and%20avoid%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20games.%20So%20these%20things%20are%20happening%2C%20and%20it%20is%20a%20fact.%20But%20I%20do%20not%20blame%20the%20players%20outright%3B%20we%20are%20all%20equally%20guilty%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709364540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F3gc31udc_ishan-kishan-shreyas-iyer_625x300_24_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Feveryone-should-fall-in-place-ex-india-stars-brutal-take-on-ishan-kishan-shreyas-iyer-contract-row-5155028%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BCCI%20had%20warned%20the%20centrally%20contracted%20players%20not%20to%20skip%20domestic%20games%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20move%20could%20lead%20to%20%26quot%3Bsever%20repercussions%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mark%20Zuckerberg%20shares%20new%20pics%20from%20Ambani%20bash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709364173000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108157586%2Cimgsize-81060.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmark-zuckerberg-and-priscilla-chan-attend-anant-ambani-and-radhika-merchants-pre-wedding-