%20to%20ensure%20peaceful%20demonstrations%20are%20not%20hijacked%20by%20extremist%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImmigrants%20who%20have%20come%20here%20have%20integrated%20and%20contributed.%20They%20have%20helped%20write%20the%20latest%20chapter%20in%20our%20island%20story.%20They%20have%20done%20this%20without%20being%20required%20to%20give%20up%20their%20identity%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rishi%20Sunak%20in%20a%20speech%20outside%2010%20Downing%20Street.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20be%20a%20practising%20Hindu%20and%20a%20proud%20Briton%20as%20I%20am%2C%20or%20a%20devout%20Muslim%20and%20a%20patriotic%20citizen%20as%20so%20many%20are%2C%20or%20a%20committed%20Jewish%20person%20and%20the%20heart%20of%20your%20local%20community%2C%20and%20all%20underpinned%20by%20the%20tolerance%20of%20our%20established%2C%20Christian%20church%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20fear%20that%20our%20great%20achievement%20in%20building%20the%20world's%20most%20successful%20multi-ethnic%2C%20multi%20faith%20democracy%20is%20being%20deliberately%20undermined.%20There%20are%20forces%20here%20at%20home%20trying%20to%20tear%20us%20apart%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20speaking%20soon%20after%20what%20he%20characterised%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bbeyond%20alarming%26quot%3B%20win%20in%20a%20bye-election%20on%20Thursday%20of%20a%20controversial%20politician%2C%20George%20Galloway%2C%20in%20Greater%20Manchester%20following%20a%20campaign%20dominated%20by%20the%20divisions%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20on%20too%20many%20occasions%20recently%2C%20the%20streets%20of%20Britain%20had%20been%20hijacked%20by%20small%20groups%20who%20are%20hostile%20to%20British%20values%20and%20have%20no%20respect%20for%20its%20democratic%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIslamist%20extremists%20and%20the%20far%20right%20feed%20off%20and%20embolden%20each%20other.%20They%20are%20equally%20desperate%20to%20pretend%20that%20their%20violence%20is%20somehow%20justified%20when%20actually%20these%20groups%20are%20two%20sides%20of%20the%20same%20extremist%20coin%E2%80%A6%20both%20loathe%20the%20pluralist%2C%20modern%20country%20we%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20stressed%20that%20both%20these%20groups%20of%20extremists%20were%20spreading%20the%20poison%20of%20extremism%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20draining%20Britain's%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BNo%20country%20is%20perfect%2C%20but%20I%20am%20enormously%20proud%20of%20the%20good%20that%20our%20country%20has%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20stand%20here%20as%20our%20country's%20first%20non-white%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20leading%20the%20most%20diverse%20government%20in%20our%20country's%20history%20to%20tell%20people%20of%20all%20races%2C%20all%20faiths%20and%20all%20backgrounds%20it%20is%20not%20the%20colour%20of%20your%20skin%2C%20the%20God%20you%20believe%20in%20or%20where%20you%20were%20born%2C%20that%20will%20determine%20your%20success%20but%20just%20your%20own%20hard%20work%20and%20endeavour.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishi%20Sunak%20reiterated%20his%20support%20for%20a%20new%20protocol%20agreed%20with%20the%20police%20forces%20of%20the%20country%20earlier%20this%20week%20to%20take%20action%20against%20violent%20activities%20that%20threaten%20the%20personal%20security%20of%20members%20of%20Parliament%20and%20also%20any%20violence%20during%20serial%20protests%20taking%20place%20in%20response%20to%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict.%20He%20said%20threats%20of%20violence%20and%20intimidation%20are%20alien%20to%20the%20British%20way%20of%20doing%20things%20and%20must%20be%20resisted%20at%20all%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20this%20country.%20My%20family%20and%20I%20owe%20it%20so%20much.%20The%20time%20has%20now%20come%20for%20us%20all%20to%20stand%20together%20to%20combat%20the%20forces%20of%2