ies%20of%20violence%2C%20the%20helplessness%20of%20victims%2C%20their%20echoing%2C%20pleading%20voices%20and%20testimonies%20lay%20siege%20to%20his%20mind%2C%20he%20disintegrates.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECows%20and%20tribal%20politics%3A%20Anil%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EGausevak%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnil%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20novella%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGausevak%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20portrays%20how%20political%20patronage%20has%20overturned%20the%20earlier%20solidarities%20of%20workers%20and%20downtrodden.%20Now%2C%20the%20tribals%20must%20either%20get%20%E2%80%9Cintegrated%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnew%20system%E2%80%9D%20or%20get%20killed%20in%20encounters.%20An%20ordinary%20college%20going%20tribal%20youth%20Dhama%20Chero%2C%20manages%20to%20become%20a%20local%20panchayat%20level%20leader%2C%20and%20then%20dons%20the%20mantle%20of%20a%20cow%20protector%2C%20hoping%20it%20will%20enable%20him%20to%20get%20Hindu%20Party%20ticket%20to%20contest%20MLA%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20blessings%20of%20the%20Goddess%20of%20Greed%2C%20a%20stiff%20competition%20went%20on%20among%20the%20police%20to%20extort%20more%2C%20and%20the%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ecattle%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E)%20traders%2C%20to%20save%20more.%20The%20traders%20found%20newer%20ways%20to%20cross%20the%20police%20barriers%2C%20while%20the%20police%20tried%20to%20enter%20as%20many%20trucks%20as%20possible%20to%20check%20health%20documents%20of%20the%20animals%20and%20the%20arrangements%20for%20their%20fodder%20and%20water.%20Any%20laxity%20led%20to%20a%20case%20lodged%20under%20specific%20clauses%20of%20Prevention%20of%20Cruelty%20to%20Animals%20Act%2C%20due%20to%20which%20the%20animals%20were%20held%20back%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20But%20the%20business%20never%20stopped.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20work%20for%20the%20country%20on%20a%20more%20dependable%20basis%2C%20Dhama%20Chero%20had%2C%20thanks%20to%20his%20politics%2C%20set%20up%20a%20cow-shelter%2C%20and%20was%20now%20a%20registered%20cow-protector%2C%20%E2%80%9Cgausevak.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20mechanics%20that%20connect%20cow%20politics%20to%20upward%20mobility%20and%20quick%20profits%20are%20laid%20bare.%20Opting%20out%20of%20this%20politics%20can%20reduce%20a%20man%20to%20mere%20fodder%20in%20the%20perpetual%20brutal%20struggle%20between%20the%20State%20and%20the%20Naxalites.%20And%20yet%2C%20the%20price%20of%20co-option%20also%20keeps%20getting%20raised%20for%20ambitious%20youth%20like%20Dhama%20Chero.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20these%20Hindi%20novels%2C%20the%20eye%20watching%20the%20march%20of%20events%20is%20not%20that%20of%20a%20baffled%20outsider%2C%20but%20of%20an%20insider%3B%20of%20someone%20caught%20in%20a%20nightmare%20they%20have%20no%20ability%20to%20control.%20Like%20Partition%20narratives%2C%20these%20stories%20record%2C%20bear%20witness%2C%20and%20also%20lament%20for%20simpler%2C%20more%20innocent%20times%20when%20all%20shades%20of%20humanity%20could%20exist%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20fact%20way.%20With%20courage%20and%20forthrightness%2C%20they%20perform%20the%20first%20duty%20of%20literature%3A%20%E2%80%9CTo%20tell%20us%20the%20truth%20about%20ourselves%20by%20telling%20us%20lies%20about%20other%20people.%E2%80%9D%20They%20create%20not%20just%20psychic%20spaces%2C%20but%20initiate%20a%20much%20needed%20moral%20discourse%20about%20experiences%20that%20get%20buried%20in%20the%20noise%20of%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERashwita%20Ravy%20is%20the%20pen%20name%20of%20the%20author%2C%20a%20literature%20lover.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709346611000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26130445%2FIMG_2925-3.