0India%20or%20Bharat%20as%20they%20prefer%20to%20call%20it%20today.%20To%20my%20mind%2C%20both%20positions%20are%20problematic.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20criticism%20that%20the%20compulsory%20registration%20process%2C%20six%20months%20into%20or%20out%20of%20a%20partnership%2C%20infringes%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%20and%20illegitimately%20criminalises%20and%20infantilises%20adult%20relations%2C%20does%20not%20go%20far%20enough.%20Divested%20of%20all%20culpability%2C%20the%20underlying%20cultural%20presumptions%20of%20the%20regulation%20have%20not%20come%20up%20for%20public%20discussion%20at%20all.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20live-in%20relationship%20in%20India%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20be%20very%20clear%2C%20rides%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20moral%20and%20statistical%20norm%20of%20heterosexual%20marriage%2C%20obligatorily%20%E2%80%9Carranged%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eeven%20by%20oneself%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewith%20the%20%E2%80%98correct%E2%80%99%20person%20of%20the%20opposite%20sex.%20The%20parental%20and%20community%20surveillance%20the%20UCC%20authorises%20for%20the%20live-in%20relationship%20is%20not%20very%20different%20from%20that%20already%20in%20place%20for%20the%20Indian%20arranged%20marriage.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPenal%20intrusion%20into%20the%20bedrooms%20of%20adult%20persons%20%E2%80%98living%20in%20sin%E2%80%99%20is%20possible%20to%20outsource%20in%20a%20society%20which%20polices%20the%20bedrooms%20adults%20can%20or%20cannot%20enter%20via%20marriage.%20Middle%20class%20%E2%80%98woke%E2%80%99%20rhetoric%20has%20been%20quick%20to%20cancel%20the%20anachronism%20of%20one%20but%20not%20the%20other.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20statistical%20incidence%20of%20free%20spirits%20entering%20bohemian%20relationships%20with%20partners%20they%20are%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eallowed%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20marry%2C%20remains%20next%20to%20negligible%20in%20India.%20The%20regulatory%20harassment%20is%20really%20that%20of%20a%20separate%20minority%20of%20couples%20made%20up%20of%20predominantly%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Emixed%20caste%2C%20mixed%20faith%20or%20otherwise%20%E2%80%98wrong%E2%80%99%20partners%2C%20cohabiting%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98cringeworthy%E2%80%99%20manner.%20It%20makes%20political%20sense%20for%20the%20state%20to%20keep%20tabs%20on%20them%2C%20only%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20majoritarian%20marriage%20%E2%80%93%20a%20parentally%20blessed%2C%20public%2C%20celebratory%20and%20endogamous%20union.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIronically%2C%20for%20a%20government%20which%20wants%20to%20de-colonise%20India%2C%20the%20emphasis%20on%20marriage%20as%20the%20only%20healthy%20and%20normal%20sexual%2C%20cohabiting%20relationship%20possible%20between%20two%20adults%20%E2%80%93%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20%E2%80%93%20remains%20an%20imperial%20legacy.%20Indeed%2C%20as%20my%20own%20research%20has%20shown%2C%20for%20the%20post%20Mutiny%20Crown%20government%20of%201857%2C%20the%20quest%20for%20uniformity%20was%20itself%20a%20punitive%20strategy%20by%20which%20to%20civilise%2C%20sanitise%20and%20subdue%20a%20defiant%20and%20extremely%20diverse%20native%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Esociety.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEnforcing%20western%20conjugal%20adult%20norms%20of%20monogamy%20was%20predicated%2C%20however%2C%20on%20a%20colossal%20error%20%E2%80%93%20the%20confusion%20of%20the%20vast%20and%20bewildering%20variety%20of%20pre-pubertal%20sacramental%20%E2%80%98marriages%E2%80%99%20extant%20in%20India%20as%20unions%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20the%20same%20kind%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20the%20rulers%E2%80%99%20own%20%E2%80%93%20legal%20contracts%20involving%20long%20engagements%2C%20mutual%20consent%20and%20the%20necessity%20for%20%E2%80%98love%E2%80%99%20to%20morally%20justify%20adult%20sexual%20cohabitation.%20In%20reality%2C%20the%20Victorian%20and%20the%20Hindu%20unions%20were%20not%20logically%20comparable%20at%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20rituals%20of%20marriage%20which%20all%20clean%2C%20caste%20Hindu%20girls%20underwent%2C%20bore%20no%20immediate%2C%20intrinsic%20or%20inherent%20connection%20with%20heterosexual%20love%20or%20even%20sexual%20consummation.%20Cross-culturally%20speaking%2C%20they%20were%20more%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20baptisms.%20Boys%20performed%20the%20sacred%20thread%20ceremony%2C%20girls%20performed%20the%20%E2%80%98marriage%E2%80%99%20ceremony%2C%20to%20count%20as%20full%20members%20of%20a%20particular%20caste%20society.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20is%20why%20even%20the%20%E2%80%98diverse%E2%80%99%20counter-intuitive%2C%20matrilineal%20customs%20of%20marriage%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20to%20an%20absconding%20bridegroom%2C%20or%20to%20a%20deity%20or%20a%20sword%20or%20to%20a%20Brahmin%20guru%20from%20a%20different%20household%20%E2%80%93%20were%20all%20pre-pubertal%20and%20totally%20respectable%20community%20events.%20One%20only%20needs%20to%20have%20watched%20ITV%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDownton%20Abbey%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20understand%20the%20colossal%20difference%20between%20the%20traditional%20variety%20of%20Hindu%20ceremonies%20and%20the%20uniform%20English%20understanding%20of%20marriage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENever%20ones%20to%20balk%20however%2C%20the%20imperial%20rulers%20rushed%20in%20where%20angels%20fear%20to%20tread.%20The%20obnoxious%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EContagious%20Diseases%20Act%20(CDA)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%201868%2C%20was%20unleashed%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20stamp%20out%20all%20but%20western%20styled%20nuclear%2C%20male%20headed%20family%20systems.%20Unions%20not%20focused%20around%20the%20heterosexual%20marital%20couple%20were%20stigmatised%20as%20perpetuators%20of%20promiscuity%2C%20polygamy%2C%20even%20%E2%80%9Chereditary%E2%80%9D%20prostitution.%20%E2%80%9CUnmarried%E2%80%9D%20women%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20abandoned%20widows%20or%20poorer%2C%20vagrant%2C%20less%20privileged%20single%20women%20%E2%80%93%20were%20incarcerated%20in%20Lock%20Hospitals%20as%20a%20source%20of%20venereal%20disease%20for%20British%20soldiers%20in%20cantonments%2C%20unaccompanied%20by%20wives%20under%20law.%20The%20Act%20however%20was%20condemned%20in%20Britain%20itself%20and%20finally%20repealed%20in%201886%20through%20the%20efforts%20of%20British%20suffragettes%2C%20its%20draconian%20business%20in%20India%20left%20half%20finished.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20second%20weapon%20aimed%20at%20standardising%20the%20Hindu%20family%20systems%20to%20meet%20the%20western%20norm%2C%20was%20the%20Age%20of%20Consent%20Bill%20(1891)%2C%20which%20sought%20to%20portray%20pre-pubertal%20marriage%20ceremonies%20as%20in%20fact%20perpetuating%20pederasty%20and%20criminal%20rape.%20But%20here%20too%2C%20after%20many%20long%20years%20of%20protest%20and%20Assembly%20deliberations%2C%20now%20by%20the%20upper%20castes%2C%20the%20government%20only%20managed%20an%20escalation%20of%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20from%20the%20existing%2010%20to%2012%20years!%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bill%E2%80%99s%20civilisational%20purpose%2C%20however%2C%20had%20been%20served%20%E2%80%93%20to%20demean%20the%20Hindus%20for%20bestiality%20towards%20child%20wives%20and%20women.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EStoked%20into%20nationalist%20anger%20over%20the%20Bill%2C%20Tilak%E2%80%99s%20Home%20Rule%20agitation%20(1916)%20and%20later%20The%20Sarada%20Act%20of%201928%2C%20under%20a%20triumphant%20native%20leadership%20now%2C%20put%20an%20end%20to%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20controversy%20by%20removing%20the%20justification%20for%20%E2%80%9Cchild%20marriage%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20the%20bar%20was%20raised%20to%20a%20clear%20post-menarche%20age%20of%2014%20for%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20child%20marriage%2C%20in%20its%20original%20pre-pubertal%20sacramental%20sense%2C%20is%20illicitly%20followed%20by%20some%20communities%20but%20by%20and%20large%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esamskari%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20obligation%20that%20a%20girl%E2%80%99s%20first%20menarche%20must%20be%20preceded%20by%20a%20baptismal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eceremony%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20marriage%20has%20thankfully%20lost%20its%20sacred%20force.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%2C%20then%2C%20the%20continual%20hiking%20of%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20post%20the%20Sarada%20Act%3F%20If%20we%20are%20to%20go%20by%20the%20authoritarian%20motivations%20of%20the%20imperial%20government%2C%20fixing%20biological%20age%20limits%20to%20the%20formal%20or%20informal%20practice%20of%20heterosexual%20coupling%20achieves%20%E2%80%9Cuniformity%E2%80%9D%20most%20efficiently.%20Currently%2C%20the%20minimum%20age%20of%20marriage%20%E2%80%93%2018%20for%20women%20%E2%80%93%20is%20threatening%20to%20go%20up%20to%20even%2021.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20criminalise%20more%20and%20more%20%E2%80%98wrong%E2%80%99%20unions%20as%20forms%20of%20%E2%80%9Cchild%20marriage%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20criminal%20law%20courts%E2%80%99%20repeated%20advisory%20that%20the%20government%20rethink%20lowering%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20has%20gone%20unheard.%20The%20persecution%20in%20Assam%20of%20many%20young%2C%20%E2%80%98differently%E2%80%99%20married%20men%2C%20as%20criminal%20rapists%20of%20technically%20underage%20but%20sexually%20mature%20wives%2C%20continues.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECharges%20of%20rape%20are%20largely%20initiated%20by%20parents%20of%20the%20girls%2C%20despite%20their%20protestations%20in%20court%20that%20the%20relationship%20was%20consensual%20and%20one%20of%20love.%20Now%20with%20the%20Uttarakhand%20UCC%2C%20the%20surveillance%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eadult%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20live%20in%20relationships%2C%20will%20bring%20in%20more%20and%20more%20%E2%80%98wrong%E2%80%99%20unions%20into%20the%20ambit%20of%20criminal%20prosecution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20post-colonial%2C%20largely%20virginal%2C%20legal%20marriage%20of%20today%20bears%20the%20marks%20of%20good%20old%20Indian%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejugaad%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Thankfully%2C%20it%20is%20not%20child%20marriage%20any%20more.%20But%20equally%2C%20is%20it%20morally%20and%20not%20merely%20biologically%2C%20%E2%80%98adult%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20astonishing%20statistic%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcensusindia.gov.in%2Fcensus.website%2Fdata%2Fcensus-tables%5C%22%3Ealmost%20the%20entire%20female%20population%20in%20the%20critical%20age%20group%20of%2025-29%20is%20married%3C%2Fa%3E%20(94.3%25%20according%20to%202001%20census%20and%2091.2%25%20in%202011)%2C%20points%20to%20traditional%20obligatory%2C%20family%20and%20community%20sentiments%20behind%20the%20%E2%80%98child%20marriage%E2%80%99%20of%20yore%20having%20carried%20over%20into%20the%20modern%2C%20adult%20avatar%20as%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20UCC%E2%80%99s%20assumption%2C%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20gender%20rights%2C%20that%20young%20women%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20face%20a%20brutal%20fate%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20their%20live-in%20lovers%20is%20skewed.%20Matching%20the%20high%20percentage%20of%20the%20population%20of%20women%20that%20are%20married%20in%20India%2C%20is%20the%20other%2C%20dismally%20high%20percentage%20of%20married%20women%20who%20take%20their%20own%20lives%2C%20compared%20to%20other%20cultures%2C%20testifying%20to%20the%20pressure%20to%20not%20only%20marry%20but%20to%20stay%20married.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENational%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%E2%80%99s%20data%20on%20%E2%80%98accidental%20deaths%20and%20suicides%E2%80%99%20records%20that%20between%202014%20and%202020%2C%20women%20who%20were%20currently%20married%20accounted%20for%20a%20whopping%2063%C2%B71%25%20(28%2C085%20of%2044%2C498)%20suicide%20deaths%20among%20women%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMarriage%20in%20India%20unfortunately%20does%20not%20ensure%20a%20more%20protected%2C%20happier%20young%20womanhood.%20The%20suffering%20of%20women%20routinely%20violated%2C%20killed%20and%20even%20burnt%20within%20the%20sacred%20legal%20confines%20of%20marriage%20cannot%20be%20denied%20a%20voice%20and%20strategically%20wished%20away%20to%20justify%20UCC%E2%80%99s%20uncalled%20for%20regulation%20of%20informal%20unions.%20Under%20criminal%20law%2C%20the%20death%20or%20harassment%20of%20a%20woman%20within%20the%20first%20seven%20years%20of%20marriage%20makes%20a%20man%20automatically%20vulnerable%20to%20charges%20of%20domestic%20violence%2C%20even%20murder%20and%20dowry%20death.%20The%20realities%20of%20a%20young%20bride%2C%20living%20with%20a%20husband%20who%20is%20really%20a%20stranger%2C%20under%20the%20control%20of%20his%20own%20parental%20household%2C%20is%20there%20for%20everyone%20to%20see%20in%20this%20legal%20prescription.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20India%2C%20almost%20all%20women%20are%20born%2C%20menstruate%20and%20marry%20under%20the%20benevolent%20and%20benign%20dictatorship%20of%20parents.%20In%20such%20a%20context%2C%20the%20Uttarakhand%20UCC%E2%80%99s%20determined%20attempt%20to%20put%20the%20screws%20on%20free%20consensual%20living%20together%2C%20based%20on%20love%20and%20mutual%20attraction%20between%20an%20adult%20man%20and%20woman%2C%20is%20not%20entirely%20surprising.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAmrit%20Srinivasan%20is%20a%20sociologist%2C%20formerly%20a%20Professor%20at%20the%20IIT-%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709308753000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18112019%2FFEE464CC-1368-48CB-AF2D-1EA659E84547.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Futtrakhands-uniform-civil-code-is-a-mere-extension-of-highly-controlled-lives-indian-women-lead%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20India%2C%20almost%20all%20women%20are%20born%2C%20menstruate%20and%20marry%20under%20the%20benevolent%20and%20benign%20dictatorship%20of%20parents.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20Uttarakhand's%20recent%20legislative%20outreach%20on%20live-in%20relationships%20doesn't%20come%20as%20a%20surprise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Futtrakhands-uniform-civil-code-is-a-mere-extension-of-highly-controlled-lives-indian-women-lead%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22FIU%20imposes%20Rs%205.49%20cr%20penalty%20on%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20for%20PMLA%20violations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709308250000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-02%2F05%2Ffull%2F1707154504-4958.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ffiu-imposes-rs-5-49-cr-penalty-on-paytm-payments-bank-for-pmla-violations-124030101100_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20scrutiny%20of%20documents%2C%20FIU%20had%20issued%20a%20compliance%20Show%20Cause%20Notice%20to%20the%20bank%20for%20its%20violations%20of%20PML%20rules%2C%20including%20Know%20Your%20Customer%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ffiu-imposes-rs-5-49-cr-penalty-on-paytm-payments-bank-for-pmla-violations-124030101100_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ffiu-imposes-rs-5-49-cr-penalty-on-paytm-payments-bank-for-pmla-violations-124030101100_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3