F%5C%22%3Eonly%20the%20national%20flag%20and%20the%20flag%20of%20Karnataka%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20permitted%20to%20be%20hoisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20accused%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20of%20diverting%20money%20from%20Hindu%20temples%20to%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20minority%20community.%20Along%20with%20this%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20Congress%20government%20of%20Karnataka%20was%20appointing%20non-Hindus%20in%20the%20temple%20trusts%20by%20amending%20the%20Hindu%20Religious%20Institutions%20%26amp%3B%20Charitable%20Endowments%20Act%2C%201997%2C%20and%20taking%2010%25%20of%20the%20donations%20received%20by%20Hindu%20temples%20as%20tax.%20It%20is%20also%20claimed%20that%20according%20to%20the%20amendment%2C%20donations%20received%20by%20temples%20and%20others%20can%20also%20be%20used%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20any%20religious%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20four%20related%20but%20distinct%20claims%20in%20these%20allegations%2C%20which%3Cem%3E%20Alt%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%20investigate%20in%20this%20report%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHas%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20started%20taxing%20Hindu%20temples%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIs%20the%20amount%20collected%20as%20tax%20on%20donations%20to%20Hindu%20temples%20(10%25)%20being%20used%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20%E2%80%98any%E2%80%99%20religion%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIs%20money%20collected%20from%20Hindu%20temples%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20being%20diverted%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20minority%20communities%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHas%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20amended%20the%20laws%20and%20introduced%20a%20provision%20to%20appoint%20non-Hindus%20in%20temple%20trusts%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews18%20anchor%20Rahul%20Shivshankar%20tweeted%20on%20February%2016%20that%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20Karnataka%20had%20allocated%20Rs%20330%20crore%20in%20the%20Budget%20for%20the%20development%2