2%3ERishi%20Bagree%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMeghUpdates%2Fstatus%2F1760582918764957786%5C%22%3EMegh%20Updates%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20among%20those%20who%20amplified%20the%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%3E%3Cb%3EFact%20check%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDid%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20begin%20taxing%20Hindu%20temples%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20did%20not%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20introduce%20the%20tax%20on%20Hindu%20temples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Common%20Pool%20Fund%20was%20started%20in%202003%20when%20the%20Hindu%20Religious%20Institutions%20%26amp%3B%20Charitable%20Endowments%20Act%2C%201997%20came%20into%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20Section%2017%20of%20this%20law%20was%20amended%20and%20a%20provision%20was%20made%20to%20collect%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20the%20funds%20generated%20by%20high%20income%20temples%20to%20provide%20assistance%20to%20low%20income%20temples%20under%20the%20Common%20Pool%20Fund.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20B.S.%20Yediyurappa%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20representing%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Common%20Pool%20Fund%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Common%20Pool%20Fund%20has%20been%20described%20in%20detail%20in%20Chapter%204%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Religious%20Institutions%20and%20Charitable%20Endowments%20Act%2C%201997.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Dharmarika%20Parishad%20has%20the%20power%20to%20create%20a%20common%20pool%20fund%20in%20which%20a%20small%20part%20of%20the%20income%20of%20big%20temples%20and%20grants%20received%20from%20the%20state%20government%20would%20be%20contributed%20for%20the%20maintenance%20of%20small%20and%20low%20income%20Hindu%20temples%2C%20and%20religious%20institutions%20of%20Hindus%20falling%20within%20the%20Muzrai%20department.%20Grants%20were%20created%20to%20build%20orphanages%20for%20Hindus%2C%20construction%20of%20cowsheds%2C%20the%20study%20of%20the%20Hindu%20religion%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20amendment%20made%20in%202011%2C%20the%20tax%20rates%20on%20temples%20were%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E0%25%20of%20the%20income%20of%20temples%20whose%20annual%20income%20was%20less%20than%20Rs%205%20lakh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E5%25%20of%20the%20net%20income%20of%20temples%20whose%20annual%20income%20exceeded%20Rs%205%20lakh%20but%20did%20not%20exceed%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E10%25%20of%20the%20net%20income%20of%20temples%20whose%20annual%20income%20was%20more%20than%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20new%20amendment%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20is%20no%20common%20pool%20fund%20for%20temples%20whose%20annual%20income%20is%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFor%20temples%20with%20an%20annual%20income%20between%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20to%20Rs%201%20crore%2C%20a%20total%20of%205%25%20of%20their%20annual%20income%20would%20go%20to%20the%20common%20pool%20fund.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFor%20temples%20with%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20and%20above%2C%20a%20total%20of%2010%25%20would%20go%20to%20the%20common%20pool%20fund.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20source%20working%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20shared%20a%20file%20with%20%3Cem%3EAlt%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20documents%20the%20past%20and%20present%20changes%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20Hindu%20Religious%20Institutions%20%26amp%3B%20Charitable%20Endowments%20Act%201997%20Amendment%20Bill.%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.altnews.in%2Fs%2FmfR7qE98r2b8ccp%5C%22%3EComplete%20file%3C%2Fa%3E)%20It%20can%20be%20clearly%20seen%20from%20the%20invocation%20of%20Section%2017%20of%20this%20law%20that%20the%20Common%20Pool%20Fund%20had%20been%20in%20force%20since%202003%2C%20and%20was%20changed%20in%202011%20when%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Yediyurappa%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20as%20well%2C%205%20to%2010%25%20of%20the%20total%20annual%20income%20of%20high%20income%20temples%20used%20to%20go%20to%20the%20common%20pool%20fund.%20In%20the%20later%20change%2C%20only%20the%20income%20band%20was%20revised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F01181503%2Fimage-1889.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22755%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F01181503%2Fimage-1889.png%20755w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F01181503%2Fimage-1889-300x170.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699681%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22428%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20found%20an%20article%20published%20on%20May%209%2C%202011%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fmembers-of-hindu-janajagruthi-samiti-staged-a-protest-outside-the-office-of-deputy-commissioner-in-mangalore-on-monday-to-protest-what-they-described-as-the-unwarranted-interference-of-the-bjp-led-state-government-in-to-the-affairs-of-hindu-religious-institutions-in-karnataka-they-urged-the-governor-h-r-bhardwaj-not-to-give-his-assent-to-the-karnataka-hindu-religious-institutions-and-charitable-endowments-amendment-bill-2011-%2Farticleshow%2F8207788.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20website%20covering%20how%20the%20Hindu%20Jan%20Jagruti%20Samiti%20protested%20against%20the%20BJP%20government%20and%20urged%20the%20governor%20to%20refuse%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20amendment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%2010%25%20of%20temple%20donations%20collected%20as%20tax%20used%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20%E2%80%98any%E2%80%99%20religion%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2010%25%20alleged%20tax%20which%20is%20being%20discussed%20in%20the%20viral%20claims%20is%20actually%20not%20a%20common%20tax%20collected%20by%20the%20government.%20Instead%2C%20this%20amount%20goes%20into%20the%20common%20pool%20fund%20only.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20the%20money%20from%20the%20Common%20Pool%20Fund%20be%20used%20for%20other%20religions%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20as%20per%20Section%2019(2)(ii)%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Religious%20Institutions%20%26amp%3B%20Charitable%20Endowments%20Act%2C%201997%2C%20the%20Common%20Pool%20Fund%20shall%20be%20so%20administered%20that%20contributions%20and%20donations%20made%20to%20any%20institution%20or%20institution%20of%20any%20religious%20denomination%20or%20any%20section%20would%20be%20utilized%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20that%20particular%20class%20or%20denomination%20or%20section%20only.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20money%20from%20the%20common%20pool%20fund%20of%20Hindu%20temples%20could%20be%20used%20only%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F01181848%2Fimage-1890.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22752%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F01181848%2Fimage-1890.png%20752w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F01181848%2Fimage-1890-300x81.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699682%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22202%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20the%20money%20taken%20from%20Hindu%20temples%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20being%20diverted%20to%20the%20welfare%20of%20minority%20communities%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20government%E2%80%99s%20Muzrai%20minister%20Ramalinga%20Reddy%2C%20responding%20to%20BJP%20MP%20Tejasvi%20Surya%E2%80%99s%20allegations%2C%20tweeted%20that%20Muzrai%20department%20money%20could%20be%20used%20only%20on%20temples%20and%20minority%20welfare%20department%20money%20could%20only%20be%20used%20on%20minority%20buildings%20and%20religious%20places.%20He%20insisted%20no%20money%20from%20the%20temples%20had%20been%20given%20to%20the%20minority%20welfare%20department.%20Along%20with%20this%2C%20the%20Muzrai%20minister%20called%20the%20viral%20claim%20false%20and%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20members%20were%20experts%20in%20misleading%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBJP4India%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40BJP4India%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTejasvi_Surya%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Tejasvi_Surya%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Money%20from%20the%20endowment%20department%20can%20only%20be%20used%20on%20temples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Money%20from%20the%20minority%20welfare%20department%20can%20only%20be%20used%20on%20minority%20buildings%20and%20religious%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20No%20money%20from%20temples%20has%20been%20given%20to%20the%20minority%20welfare%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FpPje3vb5m1%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FpPje3vb5m1%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Ramalinga%20Reddy%20(%40RLR_BTM)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRLR_BTM%2Fstatus%2F1758425817514914303%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2016%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20news%20outlet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fkarnataka%2Fan-editor-gave-the-karnataka-budget-a-communal-spin-but-heres-what-the-numbers-say%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Reddy%20stated%20that%20the%20government%20had%20no%20control%20over%20the%20temples.%20He%20explained%20that%20budget%20funds%20allocated%20for%20the%20Muzrai%20Department%20since%202011%20were%20entirely%20utilised%20for%20the%20development%20of%20all%20categories%20of%20temples%20falling%20under%20it.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20amount%20allocated%20in%20the%20budget%20for%20the%20Minority%20Welfare%20Department%20was%20used%20solely%20for%20religious%20and%20cultural%20welfare%20activities%20of%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAlt%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20contacted%20Rajendra%20Kataria%2C%20the%20principal%20secretary%20to%20the%20Karnataka%20government%E2%80%99s%20revenue%20department%2C%20for%20more%20information.%20He%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20about%2035%2C000%20temples%20under%20the%20Muzrai%20department.%20These%20temples%20are%20divided%20into%20A%2C%20B%20and%20C%20categories%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20income%20and%20property.%20Temples%20with%20incomes%20more%20than%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20are%20Category%20A%2C%20with%20a%20total%20of%20205%20temples.%20Temples%20with%20incomes%20ranging%20from%20Rs%205%20to%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20are%20categorised%20under%20the%20B%20category%2C%20consisting%20of%20193%20temples.%20Finally%2C%20those%20generating%20an%20income%20less%20than%20Rs%205%20lakh%20are%20placed%20in%20the%20C%20category%2C%20making%20up%2034%2C165%20temples.%20The%20government%20does%20not%20take%20money%20from%20these%20temples.%20Money%20from%20the%20donation%20boxes%20(Hundi)%20is%20drawn%20by%20the%20local%20committees%20and%20deposited%20in%20the%20bank%20accounts%20of%20the%20respective%20temples%2C%20which%20is%20used%20by%20the%20temples%20for%20their%20management%2C%20organising%20programs%2C%20development%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20etc.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBigger%20temples%20have%20a%20local%20official%20in%20whose%20presence%20the%20donation%20box%20is%20opened%20by%20the%20committee%20and%20this%20money%20is%20deposited%20in%20his%20account%20only.%20This%20money%20does%20not%20go%20to%20the%20government.%20The%20work%20of%20the%20Muzrai%20department%20of%20the%20government%20is%20to%20provide%20financial%20assistance%20to%20these%20temples%20for%20their%20development.%20The%20government%20also%20makes%20arrangements%20for%20the%20convenience%20of%20devotees%2C%20such%20as%20the%20opening%20of%20guest%20houses%20for%20pilgrims.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20religious%20sites%20like%20Tirupati%2C%20Varanasi%2C%20Srisailam%2C%20Mantralayam%2C%20and%20Tuljapur.%20Misinformation%20is%20being%20spread%20on%20social%20media%20that%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20takes%20money%20from%20Hindu%20temples%20and%20uses%20it%20to%20fund%20religious%20institutions%20of%20non-Hindu%20religions.%20A%20meeting%20of%20the%20Muzrai%20department%20has%20been%20held%20regarding%20this%20issue%20and%20appropriate%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20those%20spreading%20such%20rumours.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20source%20working%20in%20the%20government%20of%20Karnataka%20sent%20us%20a%20note%20on%20the%20Amendment%20Bill%20of%20Karnataka%20Hindu%20Religious%20Institutions%20and%20Charitable%20Endowments%20Act%201997.%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.altnews.in%2Fs%2FYqRTKiaMfiTQp5a%5C%22%3EComplete%20file%3C%2Fa%3E)%20This%20note%20explains%20the%20changes%20related%20and%20their%20purpose.%20It%20is%20clearly%20written%20in%20Point%206%20of%20this%20note%20that%20the%20Archakas%20and%20temple%20employees%20of%20these%20temples%20needed%20more%20money%20to%20meet%20the%20demands%20of%20economically%20backward%20C%20grade%20institutions%20under%20the%20Common%20Pool%20Fund.%20Therefore%2C%20from%20this%20point%20of%20view%2C%20it%20was%20considered%20necessary%20to%20revise%20this%20amount.%20This%20amount%20would%20be%20used%20only%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20C%20Group%20temples%20along%20with%20the%20Archaks%20and%20employees%20of%20the%20temples.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20note%20has%20a%20list%20of%20facilities%20to%20be%20provided%20to%20the%20temple%20employees%20and%20Archaks%20under%20the%20Common%20Pool%20Fund.%20For%20example%2C%20scholarship%20to%20the%20children%20of%20Archaks%2C%20insurance%20to%20the%20temple%20employees%2C%20accommodation%20facilities%2C%20free%20trips%20to%20Kashi%20and%20South%20India%20for%20the%20families%20of%20the%20temple%20employees%2C%20a%20central%20information%20center%20for%20the%20devotees%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20clearly%20stated%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20this%20note%20that%20since%20the%20enactment%20of%20the%20Act%20in%202003%2C%20the%20Common%20Pool%20Fund%20has%20been%20used%20only%20for%20Hindu%20religious%20institutions%20and%20would%20be%20used%20only%20for%20them%20in%20the%20future.%20It%20has%20not%20been%20used%20for%20any%20other%20purpose%20or%20for%20people%20of%20other%20religions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F01182112%2Fimage-1891.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22737%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F01182112%2Fimage-1891.png%20737w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F01182112%2Fimage-1891-275x300.png%20275w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699684%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22805%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews18%20anchor%20Rahul%20Shivshankar%2C%20while%20replying%20to%20Muzrai%20minister%20Ramalinga%20Reddy%2C%20tweeted%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20saying%20that%20you%20are%20diverting%20the%20funds%20of%20Hindu%20temples.%20In%20fact%20you%20cannot%20do%20so%20as%20per%20law.%20What%20I%20am%20saying%20is%20why%20should%20any%20state%20government%20(even%20the%20BJP%20government)%20be%20in%20the%20business%20of%20using%20state%20money%20to%20develop%20maintain%20and%20upgrade%20places%20of%20places%20of%20worship%20of%20any%20denomination%3F%20Why%20should%20they%20be%20controlling%20temples%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWith%20great%20respect%20Sir%20I%20am%20not%20saying%20you%20are%20diverting%20funds%20from%20Hindu%20temples.%20In%20fact%20you%20cant%20do%20that%20by%20law%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRLR_BTM%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40RLR_BTM%3C%2Fa%3E.%20What%20I%20am%20saying%20is%20why%20should%20any%20state%20government%20(even%20BJP%20ones)%20be%20in%20the%20business%20of%20using%20state%20finances%20to%20develop%2C%20maintain%20or%20upgrade%20the%20Places%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FvXoCTtgyy0%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FvXoCTtgyy0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Rahul%20Shivshankar%20(%40RShivshankar)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRShivshankar%2Fstatus%2F1758525002758926592%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2016%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHas%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20amended%20the%20law%20and%20brought%20in%20a%20provision%20to%20appoint%20non-Hindus%20to%20the%20temple%20trust%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAlt%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20noticed%20the%20point%20highlighted%20by%20BJP%20IT%20cell%20chief%20Amit%20Malviya.%20The%20provision%20he%20highlighted%20for%20the%20appointment%20of%20non-Hindus%20to%20the%20temple%20trust%20had%20actually%20been%20enacted%20prior%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%20under%20present%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah.%20There%20have%20been%20no%20recent%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20do%20these%20lines%20state%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20management%20committee%20shall%20consist%20of%20at%20least%20one%20person%20resident%20in%20the%20locality%20where%20the%20institution%20is%20situated%3A%20Provided%20that%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20composite%20institution%2C%20members%20of%20both%20Hindu%20and%20other%20religions%20may%20be%20appointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20is%20a%20composite%20institution%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20information%20given%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Fbitstream%2F123456789%2F7825%2F1%2F33_of_2001_%2528e%2529.pdf%5C%22%3Epoint%2010A%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20definition%20of%20the%20Act%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3Ecomposite%20institution%3C%2Fem%3E%20denotes%20a%20place%20of%20worship%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20customs%20and%20traditions%20common%20and%20jointly%20maintained%20by%20Hindus%20and%20other%20religions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20is%20the%20minister%E2%80%99s%20statement%20on%20this%20issue%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%3Cem%3E%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Muzrai%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fno-diversion-of-temple-funds-let-bjp-leaders-read-law-first-ramalinga-reddy-karnataka-minister-for-transport-muzrai%2Farticleshow%2F107917058.cms%5C%22%3ERamalinga%20Reddy%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20the%20viral%20claim%20about%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20introducing%20a%20provision%20to%20appoint%20non-Hindus%20to%20temple%20trusts%20was%20misleading.%20Only%20the%20committees%20of%20Baba%20Budan%20Giri%20Dargah%20in%20Chikmagalur%20district%2C%20Bhootrai%20Chowdeshwari%20and%20Saadat%20Ali%20Dargah%20in%20Shivamogga%20district%20consisted%20of%20members%20from%20both%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20communities%20because%20people%20of%20both%20the%20religions%20prayed%20at%20these%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Bill%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20assembly%2C%20but%20due%20to%20opposition%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20JDS%2C%20it%20could%20not%20be%20passed%20in%20the%20legislative%20council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22qme%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FKarnataka%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Karnataka%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FTempleTaxBill%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23TempleTaxBill%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FbwtDEEkDGI%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FbwtDEEkDGI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20NDTV%20(%40ndtv)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fndtv%2Fstatus%2F1761087964543889496%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Akhila%20Karnataka%20Archakas%20(Priests%E2%80%99)%20Association%20supported%20the%20Bill%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20and%20said%20that%20small%20temples%20were%20short%20of%20funds.%20Along%20with%20this%2C%20it%20urged%20the%20opposition%20BJP%20to%20support%20the%20Congress%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20divert%20tax%20money%20from%20rich%20A%20grade%20temples%20to%20smaller%20temples%20for%20the%20uplift%20of%2036%2C000%20C%20grade%20temples%20in%20the%20state%2C%20categorized%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20the%20All%20Karnataka%20Hindu%20Temple%20Archaka%20(priest)%20Association%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CRight%20now%2C%20we%20are%20receiving%20a%20sum%20of%20only%20Rs%205%2C000%20as%20our%20salary%2C%20which%20is%20inclusive%20of%20puja%20materials.%20No%20one%20has%20raised%20a%20strong%20voice%20for%20us%20like%20the%20current%20Muzrai%20minister%20Ramalinga%20Reddy.%20The%20money%20from%20the%20Common%20Pool%20Fund%20will%20be%20used%20only%20for%20the%20uplift%20of%20%E2%80%98C%E2%80%99%20grade%20temples%20and%20priests.%20We%20are%20very%20happy%20with%20this%20decision.%E2%80%9D%20The%20association%20also%20decided%20to%20submit%20a%20memorandum%20to%20BJP%20and%20JD(S)%20leaders%2C%20urging%20them%20not%20to%20oppose%20the%20amendments%20of%20the%20current%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.altnews.in%2Ftruth-of-rumors-around-karnatakas-new-hindu-religious-endowments-amendment-bill%2F%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20Alt%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709307036000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F01195125%2Fimage-1892.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-is-the-karnataka-temple-tax-legislation-the-claims-counterclaims-and-facts%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20targeted%20the%20Karnataka%20Congress%20government%20and%20accused%20it%20of%20appeasement%20of%20the%20minority%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-is-the-karnataka-temple-tax-legislation-the-claims-counterclaims-and-facts%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Learn%20Pottery%20%26amp%3B%20Mandana%20Art%20at%20this%20Rajasthan%20Eco-Lodge%20That%20Runs%20on%20The%20Sun%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20renowned%20for%20its%20rich%20tapestry%20of%20diverse%20cultures%2C%20and%20one%20of%20its%20most%20vibrant%20states%20is%20Rajasthan.%20Situated%20in%20the%20northwestern%20region%20of%20the%20country%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341177%2Fchhotaram-prajapat-mud-homestay-in-salawas-village-jodhpur-rajasthan-dhurrie-making%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERajasthan%20stands%20as%20a%20testament%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20opulent%20and%20vibrant%20lifestyle%20of%20its%20rulers%20throughout%20history.%20Adorned%20with%20