79%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESet%20on%20his%20path%2C%20he%20travelled%20across%20Germany%20and%20Europe%20to%20pursue%20his%20passion%20and%20take%20part%20in%20international%20gliding%20competitions%20and%20races.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20on%20visits%20to%20Germany%20that%20I%20met%20with%20some%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F280769%2Fpune-environmentalists-convert-plastic-into-fuel-video-dr-meda-tadpatrikar-shirish-phadtare%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenvironmentalists%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20activists%20who%20harboured%20in%20me%20a%20passion%20for%20environment%20preservation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%20studied%20the%20various%20ill%20effects%20of%20mass%20tourism%20on%20a%20given%20region.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20back%20in%20the%2080s%20when%20terms%20like%20sustainability%20and%20eco-tourism%20were%20unknown%20to%20many.%20After%20achieving%20much%20in%20my%20gliding%20career%2C%20I%20started%20to%20feel%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20back%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20this%20time%2C%20his%20passion%20for%20nature%20conservation%20was%20at%20a%20peak%20and%20he%20wanted%20to%20try%20his%20hand%20at%20eco-friendly%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%201980s%2C%20my%20vision%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98different%20type%20of%20tourism%E2%80%99%20began%20to%20take%20root.%20Inspired%20and%20motivated%20by%20various%20factors%2C%20I%20embarked%20on%20this%20venture.%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20monopoly%20and%20inequitable%20distribution%20of%20tourism%20income%20in%20our%20state%20served%20as%20the%20strongest%20catalyst%2C%20propelling%20me%20to%20initiate%20a%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321442%2Fcouple-anu-dillon-ram-pratap-singh-start-chambal-boutique-safari-lo