.%20On%20that%20day%2C%20too%2C%20three%20RJD%20legislators%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20six%20Rajya%20Sabha%20candidates%20of%20different%20parties%20were%20elected%20unopposed.%20Two%20each%20were%20of%20the%20RJD%20and%20BJP%20and%20one%20each%20of%20Congress%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20raises%20a%20moot%20question%2C%20as%20to%20why%20these%20three%20MLAs%20have%20decided%20to%20jump%20on%20the%20BJP%20bandwagon%20now.%20Has%20it%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20the%20election%20for%2011%20seats%20of%20the%20Bihar%20legislative%20council%20which%20is%20scheduled%20to%20take%20place%20on%20March%2021%3F%20Those%20whose%20term%20expires%20and%20are%20seeking%20re-election%20include%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20former%20CM%20Rabri%20Devi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChanging%20scenario%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20is%20that%20by%20alluring%20these%20three%20Grand%20Alliance%20MLAs%20at%20this%20point%20of%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Eclearly%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Ewants%20to%20shift%20attention%20from%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20massive%20roadshows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20political%20pundits%20had%20till%20January%2022%20ever%20predicted%20that%20the%20scenario%20in%20Bihar%20would%20change%20so%20drastically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20months%2C%20the%20entire%20media%E2%80%99s%20attention%20was%20focused%20on%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20consecration%20in%20Ayodhya.%20Television%20channels%20and%20newspapers%20in%20Bihar%20were%20filled%20with%20the%20stories%20as%20to%20how%20five%20million%20devotees%20from%20the%20state%20would%20travel%20to%20Ayodhya%20in%20days%20and%20weeks%20after%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20temple%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20This%20was%20expected%20to%20give%20a%20boost%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20prospects%20in%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll.%3C%2Fp%3