e%20launched%20his%20own%20Yatra%20on%20February%2020%2C%20the%20whole%20political%20scenario%20took%20a%20complete%20U-turn.%20The%20BJP%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20bigwigs%20were%20taken%20aback%20by%20this%20sudden%20turn%20of%20event%3Cspan%3Es%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20came%20the%20news%20that%20PM%20Modi%20would%20come%20to%20Aurangabad%20and%20Begusarai%20in%20Bihar%20on%20March%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E2.%20This%20would%20be%20preceded%20by%20a%20visit%20by%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20and%20followed%20by%3Cspan%3E%20one%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ehome%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20elsewhere%2C%20the%20media%20had%20not%20been%20giving%20due%20publicity%20to%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20activities%20in%20Bihar.%20But%20the%20turn-out%20of%20crowds%20at%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20Yatra%20had%20compelled%20it%20to%20give%20them%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERise%20in%20stature%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20that%20Tejashwi%20is%20proving%20his%20mettle%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20his%20%3Cspan%3Estill-nascent%3C%2Fspan%3E%20political%20career%20of%20eight%20years.%20In%20the%202020%20assembly%20election%20in%20Bihar%2C%20he%20single-handedly%20helped%20his%20RJD%20come%20up%20as%20the%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20assembly.%20His%20father%20was%20then%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20this%20time%20he%20is%20pulling%20more%20crowd%3Cspan%3Es%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20none%20else%20but%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20the%20top%20BJP%20leadership%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Emust%20share%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0responsib%3Cspan%3Ei%3C%2Fspan%3El%3Cspan%3Eity%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20The%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20has%20become%20a%20laughing%20stock%20because%20of%20his%20own%20self-destructive%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Emove%3C%2Fspan%3Es.%20And%20the%20BJP%20central%20leadership%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Etoo%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Ehas%2C%20by%20its%20flip-flop%20towards%20Nitish%2C%20provided%20an%20opportunity%20%3Cspan%3Ef%3C%2Fspan%3Eo%3Cspan%3Er%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Ethe%20RJD%20leader%20to%20emerge%20much%20taller%20than%20his%20stature%3Cspan%3E%20earlier.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FHh5P5mdiukw%3Fsi%3Dz54s17dFp8ksbSsm%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20the%20Modi-Shah%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0duo%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20cut%20to%20size%20all%20prominent%20faces%20of%20their%20own%20party%20in%20Bihar.%20Today%2C%20the%20party%20has%20put%20the%20responsibility%20%3Cspan%3Eof%20its%20Bihar%20unit%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eon%20Samrat%20Chaudhary%2C%20a%20party-hopper%3Cspan%3E%20himself%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Ewith%20a%20controversial%20past.%20He%20was%20sacked%20by%20the%20then-governor%20Suraj%20Bhan%20of%20Bihar%20when%20he%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Ewas%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Rabri%20Devi%20government%20in%201999.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ET%3C%2Fspan%3Ehe%20same%20BJP%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Ewas%20baying%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Efor%20his%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Eblood%20on%20the%20charge%20of%C2%A0a%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%98fake%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%20birth%20certificate.%20The%20governor%20also%20ordered%20%3Cspan%3Ethat%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Ecase%3Cspan%3Es%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0of%20fraud%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20forgery%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Ebe%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Einstituted%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20then-%3C%2Fspan%3Eleader%20of%20the%20opposition%3Cspan%3E%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%2C%20was%20in%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20campaign%20against%20him.%20A%20quarter-century%20later%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Samrat%20is%20the%20Bihar%20unit%20chief%20and%20deputy%20CM%20of%20the%20state%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3ESushil%20Modi%20is%20nowhere%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Eon%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamrat%2C%20no%20doubt%2C%20is%20young%20and%20aggressive%20and%20suits%20the%20present%20top%20brass%20of%20the%20BJP.%20But%20his%20equation%20with%20the%20senior%20leaders%2C%20especially%20those%20affiliated%20with%20the%20RSS%2C%20is%20not%20very%20smooth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20dispel%20this%20image%2C%20he%20now%20dons%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Ea%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Esaffron%20colour%3Cspan%3Eed%3C%2Fspan%3E%20turban%20%E2%80%93%3Cspan%3E%20one%20he%20had%20said%20he%20will%20take%20off%20only%20after%20ousting%20Nitish%20Kumar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709298058000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F01171701%2FBixar.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftejashwi-yatra-bihar-bjp-desperate-to-change-headlines%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20PM's%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%2C%20TV%20channels%20and%20newspapers%20in%20Bihar%20were%20filled%20with%20stories%20on%20how%20millions%20of%20devotees%20from%20the%20state%20would%20travel%20to%20Ayodhya.%20In%20contrast%2C%20a%20flood%20of%20people%20can%20now%20be%20seen%20lining%20up%20to%20see%20the%2034-year%20old%20RJD%20leader%20is%20going%20during%20his%20Yatra.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftejashwi-yatra-bihar-bjp-desperate-to-change-headlines%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Musk%20sues%20OpenAI%20for%20'perverting'%20the%20company's%20mission%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709297760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F70x70%2Fskynews-elon-musk-tesla_6441711.jpg%3F20240202120828%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Felon-musk-sues-openai-and-sam-altman-saying-company-putting-profit-over-the-public-good-13084401%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%2C%20the%20multi-billionaire%20owner%20of%20