le.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20two%20decades%20have%20passed%20since%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20details%20of%20what%20happened%20before%20the%20fire%20remain%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20on%20February%2028%2C%202002%2C%20Hindu%20mobs%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgodhra-where-the-fall-of-indias-democracy-began%5C%22%3E%20set%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fin-her-own-words-what-bilkis-bano-went-through-in-2002%5C%22%3Eblaming%20Muslims%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbbc-documentary-gujarat-2002-india-truth%5C%22%3Efor%20the%20deaths%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20pilgrims%2C%20resulting%20in%20waves%20of%20violence.%20Rapes%2C%20looting%2C%20and%20murders%20took%20place%2C%20with%20the%20Muslim%20community%20being%20the%20major%20target.%20The%20violence%20lasted%20for%20more%20than%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20state%20government%2C%20then%20headed%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20most%20of%20the%20dead%20were%20%3Cem%3Ekarsevaks%3C%2Fem%3E%20who%20had%20gone%20to%20Ayodhya%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgodhra-where-the-fall-of-indias-democracy-began%5C%22%3EGodhra%2C%20Where%20the%20Fall%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Democracy%20Began%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20peace%20for%20us%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2022%20years%2C%20Zubedabibi%20has%20been%20waiting%20for%20her%20husband%20to%20return.%20She%20has%20neither%20seen%20him%20nor%20his%20dead%20body.%20In%20Delol%20near%20Godhra%2C%20she%20lost%2045%20relatives%20to%20the%20carnage.%20Her%20relatives%20were%20murdered%2C%20maimed%2C%20and%20raped.%20Besides%20the%20pain%20of%20losing%20her%20family%2C%20her%20husband%20Mohammedbhai%20Ismailbh