ia-freedom-struggle-british-raj%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20in%20the%20railways%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Atul%20also%20started%20to%20prepare%20for%20UPSC%20CSE%20to%20become%20a%20government%20servant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%20easy%20managing%20both%20things%20and%20I%20failed%20four%20times%20before%20cracking%20the%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20served%20as%20an%20officer%2C%20conducting%20audits%20of%20national%20Navratna%20companies%20and%20Maharatna%20PSUs%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20This%20marked%20around%2013-14%20years%20into%20my%20service.%20While%20I%20enjoyed%20being%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333846%2Fhyderabad-balalatha-mallavarapu-affected-by-polio-crack-upsc-cse-without-coaching-teaches-aspirants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecivil%20servant%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20yearned%20to%20create%20something%20of%20my%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-4-1709213062.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20startup%20has%20launched%20smart%20wallet%20which%20anti-theft%20and%20enables%20you%20to%20track%20its%20location.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-4-1709213062.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-4-1709213062-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-4-1709213062-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-4-1709213062-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-4-17092130