rtunity.%20%E2%80%9CI%20decided%20to%20become%20a%20part%20of%20Atul%E2%80%99s%20vision%20and%20we%20both%20decided%20to%20collaborate%20to%20start%20Arista%20Vault%20in%202018%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Atul%20and%20Purvi%20along%20with%20their%20friend%2C%20Col%20Krishan%20Kumar%20Singh%2C%20started%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMerging%20travel%20safety%20with%20technology%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20how%20their%20brainstorming%20would%20go%2C%20Atul%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20inspired%20and%20triggered%20by%20my%20stolen%20wallet%2C%20so%20that%20is%20what%20we%20first%20tried%20to%20develop%20%E2%80%93%20a%20smart%20wallet.%20The%20smart%20wallet%20has%20a%20chip%20which%20once%20activated%20becomes%20anti-theft.%20They%20have%203000mAh%20Power%20charging%2C%20location%20tracking%20and%20RFID%20protection.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20various%20types%20of%20products%20they%20make%2C%20Purvi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CCurrently%20we%20have%20three%20categories%20of%20products.%20We%20have%20smart%20wallets%20with%20different%20price%20ranges%20and%20variants.%20We%20also%20have%20a%20bag%20with%20fingerprint%20locks.%20These%20bags%20are%20designed%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F205523%2Fdispose-electronic-electrical-waste-india-ewaste-old-laptops-batteries-phone%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20store%20your%20laptops%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20other%20valuables%20and%20can%20be%20locked%20with%20a%20fingerprint.%20Only%20the%20owner%20can%20access%20the%20bag%20once%20it%20is%20locked.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC37mvNmsDu0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20hre