20analysis%20highlighted%20that%20many%20of%20these%20VOCs%20pose%20serious%20health%20risks%2C%20including%20damage%20to%20the%20respiratory%20system%2C%20heightened%20cancer%20susceptibility%2C%20and%20adverse%20effects%20on%20developmental%20and%20reproductive%20health.%20Furthermore%2C%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EEnvironmental%20Working%20Group%3C%2Fem%3E%20(EWG)%20cautioned%20that%20the%20fumes%20emanating%20from%20certain%20cleaning%20products%20could%20trigger%20asthma%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimran%20recounts%20that%20during%20the%20first%2010%20to%2012%20weeks%20post-lockdown%2C%20she%2C%20like%20many%20other%20mothers%2C%20found%20herself%20relying%20heavily%20on%20cleaning%20products%20at%20home.%20She%20scrubbed%20surfaces%20multiple%20times%20to%20maintain%20a%20COVID-19-free%20environment.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20using%20cleaning%20liquids%20for%20washing%20our%20vegetables%2C%20fruits%20and%20everything%20else%20at%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20hygiene%20took%20centre-stage%2C%20was%20it%20unknowingly%20causing%20more%20harm%20than%20good%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20careful%20assessment%20of%20multiple%20research%20papers%20made%20Simran%20get%20up%20and%20take%20action.%20She%20looked%20for%20safer%20alternatives%2C%20but%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20many%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20same%20prices%20as%20the%20regular%20cleaning%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20becoming%20more%20aware%20of%20ingredients.%20Discovering%20many%20chemical%20names%20in%20everyday%20products%20was%20triggering%20for%20me%2C%20as%20they%20posed%20harm%20to%20my%20daughter.%20While%20doing%20home%20cleaning%2C%20I%20had%20a%20first-hand%20experience%20of%20how%20it%20was%20affecting%20my%20hands.%20I%20could%20see%20exactly%20what%20was%20being%20put%20in%20the%20bucket%2C%E2%80%9D%20Simran%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20explains%20that%20she%20realised%20that%20most%20conventional%20cleaners%20were%20laden%20with%20toxins.%20Unable%20to%20find%20any%20alternatives%2C%20she%20set%20out%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20develop%20products%20that%20would%20provide%20reassurance%20to%20mothers%20like%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeaming%20up%20with%20an%20R%26amp%3BD%20lab%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20she%20focused%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F275815%2Feco-friendly-cleaners-biodegradable-capsules-disinfectants-prevent-plastic-waste%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformulating%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20omitted%20seven%20chemicals%20known%20to%20be%20linked%20to%20health%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20ammonia%2C%20chlorine%2C%20phosphates%2C%20EDTA%20(Ethylenediaminetetraacetic%20acid)%2C%20bleach%2C%20triclosan%2C%20and%20artificial%20colours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20wanted%20her%20brand%20to%20be%20natural%2C%20she%20knew%20the%20cleaners%20had%20to%20be%20able%20to%20dislodge%20dirt%20effectively.%20So%20finding%20the%20right%20formulations%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20time-consuming%20and%20expensive%20process.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20heart%20of%20every%20cleaning%20product%20is%20the%20surfactant%20which%20dislodges%20grease%20and%20dirt%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%2C%20adding.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20to%20look%20for%20non-synthetic%20options%20for%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimran%20eventually%20discovered%20the%20solution%20in%20surfactants%20derived%20from%20coconut%20and%20sugarcane%2C%20inspiring%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Koparo%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkoparo1-1708951311.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Koparo%20is%20made%20using%20natural%20ingredients%20and%20avoids%20harmful%20chemicals%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkoparo1-1708951311.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkoparo1-1708951311-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkoparo1-1708951311-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkoparo1-1708951311-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkoparo1-1708951311-768x768.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkoparo1-1708951311-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343157%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKoparo%20is%20made%20using%20natural%20ingredients%20and%20avoids%20harmful%20chemicals%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKoparo%E2%80%99s%20products%20blend%20these%20surfactants%20with%20organic%20bio-enzymes%20and%20essential%20oils.%20After%20six%20months%20and%2010%20prototypes%20per%20product%2C%20they%20finally%20arrived%20at%20the%20winning%20combinations.%20The%20lab%20rigorously%20tested%20the%20efficacy%20of%20the%20products%2C%20and%20on%204%20February%2C%202021%2C%20Koparo%20launched%20four%20products%20%E2%80%94%20floor%20cleaner%2C%20all-purpose%20spray%2C%20hand%20wash%2C%20and%20dishwash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20another%20aspect%20that%20Simran%20says%20she%20stayed%20away%20from%20is%20artificial%20colours.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20in%20transparency%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20hide%20behind%20coloured%20packaging.%20We%20use%20no%20colours%20and%20are%20open%20about%20the%20ingredients%20we%20use.%20Additionally%2C%20our%20products%20are%20also%20100%25%20made%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%20that%20she%20was%20also%20irked%20by%20the%20advertising%20claims%20promising%20%E2%80%9Ca%20bloom%20of%20roses%E2%80%9D%20in%20your%20floor%20cleaner%20or%20the%20%E2%